od: ≥ 85%\\n62: 3. 所有关键业务逻辑都有对应的测试用例\\n63: 4. 测试代码符合 Go 最佳实践\\n64: 5. 测试可通过 `go test ./pkg/router/... ./pkg/store/... ./pkg/picod/...` 执行\\n65: 6. 无 flaky tests（确定性结果）\\n66: \\n67: ---\\n68: \\n69: ## Detailed Scope Analysis\\n70: \\n71: ### 1. router 模块\\n72: \\n73: **文件结构:**\\n74...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-040_ST-0.log:\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775883412183,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28519d05bffePfGmOIavBUovso\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7ae66084001U9dDqnelBxS9qy\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7ae64ddd0012UE61rv8NSBzGX\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28519d05bffePfGmOIavBUovso\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"toolu_7a98fe368d92444186a4db7d\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"ls -la changes/\",\"description\":\"List changes directory\"},\"output\":\"total 164\\ndrwxr-xr-x 41 root root 4096 Apr 11 12:37 .\\ndrwxr-xr-x 26 root root 4096 Apr 11 11:48 ..\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 00:35 AR-001\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 00:51 AR-002\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 01:03 AR-003\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 01:21 AR-004\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 01:33 AR-005\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 01:53 AR-006\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 02:11 AR-007\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 02:32 AR-008\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 02:51 AR-009\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 03:09 AR-010\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 03:33 AR-011\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 03:43 AR-012\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 03:59 AR-013\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 04:17 AR-014\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 04:22 AR-015\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 04:41 AR-016\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 05:33 AR-017\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 05:45 AR-018\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 06:05 AR-019\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 1