e 14: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775883379595,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2851a62e5ffe5mL8dfrsXNgAI7\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7ae5de300012J06HOg1pvjnGd\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7ae5ce1e001B0WQbYlKz3x34r\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2851a62e5ffe5mL8dfrsXNgAI7\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_3751567b51f84902ad33f118\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) - Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: > **Module:** pkg\\n4: > **Language:** Go\\n5: > **Size:** L\\n6: \\n7: ---\\n8: \\n9: ## Overview\\n10: \\n11: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing Go unit tests for three core modules:\\n12: - **pkg/router**: HTTP routing, proxy, health checking, rate limiting, authentication, session management, JWT\\n13: - **pkg/store**: Valkey/Redis-backed session and sandbox storage\\n14: - **pkg/picod**: Pico execution server with command execution and file handling\\n15: \\n16: ---\\n17: \\n18: ## Test Scenarios\\n19: \\n20: ### router 模块 - 初始化和配置\\n21: \\n22: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\\n23: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\\n24: | AR-039-001-A | router | NewRouter | Router creates with default config when nil is passed | 🔲 |\\n25: | AR-039-001-B | router | NewRouter | Router creates with custom config with SessionEnabled and JWTEnabled | 🔲 |\\n26: | AR-039-001-C | router | AddBackend/RemoveBackend | Router adds and removes backends | 🔲 |\\n27: \\n28: ### router 模块 - Backend Pool 和健康检查\\n29: \\n30: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\\n31: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\\n32: | AR-039-002