ation Report: AR-039 — Go Unit Tests (client-go)\\n\\n### Summary\\n\\n| Status | Finding |\\n|--------|---------|\\n| ❌ | **No test files exist** for the client-go library (`pkg/client/clientset/versioned/`) |\\n\\n### Spec Compliance Analysis\\n\\n| Spec Requirement | Status |\\n|------------------|--------|\\n| **Clientset** | |\\n| `Interface` with `RuntimeV1alpha1()` | ✅ Implemented |\\n| `Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface` | ❌ **Missing** |\\n| **Constructors** | |\\n| `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config)` | ✅ Implemented |\\n| `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client)` | ❌ **Missing** |\\n| `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config)` | ✅ Implemented |\\n| `New(c rest.Interface)` | ✅ Implemented |\\n| **RuntimeV1alpha1Interface** | ✅ Has RESTClient, AgentRuntimesGetter, CodeInterpretersGetter |\\n| **AgentRuntimeInterface** | |\\n| All CRUD methods | ✅ Present |\\n| `AgentRuntimeExpansion` embedded | ❌ **Not embedded** (expansion is empty but should be in interface) |\\n| **CodeInterpreterInterface** | |\\n| All CRUD methods | ✅ Present |\\n| `CodeInterpreterExpansion` embedded | ❌ **Not embedded** |\\n| **REST Defaults** | ✅ GroupVersion, APIPath, NegotiatedSerializer all correctly set |\\n\\n### Gaps\\n\\n1. **No unit tests** for the client-go library — tests need to be written for the clientset, typed clients, and expansion interfaces\\n2. `Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface` method missing from Interface\\n3. `NewForConfigAndClient` constructor missing\\n4. Expansion interfaces not embedded in typed client interfaces\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775883359366,\"end\":1775883359366}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-039_ST-4.log:\n  Line 23: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775882833579,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28522f548ffewS6xzFM6NJ4fZi\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7add8d02001hiqNwf6IVJKkrS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7add775f001K0AU5kdrnziRki\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28522f5