n33: | AR-039-002-B | router | HealthChecker.Start/Stop | Health checker monitors backends and marks unavailable | 🔲 |\n34: \n35: ### router 模块 - 限流\n36: \n37: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n38: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n39: | AR-039-003-A | router | RateLimiter.Allow | Rate limiter allows requests under limit | 🔲 |\n40: | AR-039-003-B | router | RateLimiter.Allow | Rate limiter blocks requests over limit with 429 | 🔲 |\n41: | AR-039-003-C | router | RateLimiter.Allow | Rate limiter can be disabled | 🔲 |\n42: \n43: ### router 模块 - 认证\n44: \n45: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n46: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n47: | AR-039-004-A | router | Authenticator.Middleware | Authenticator validates token correctly | 🔲 |\n48: | AR-039-004-B | router | Authenticator.Middleware | Authenticator can be disabled | 🔲 |\n49: \n50: ### router 模块 - Session 管理\n51: \n52: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n53: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n54: | AR-039-005-A | router | SessionManager | Session manager creates session | 🔲 |\n55: | AR-039-005-B | router | SessionManager | Session cleanup removes expired sessions | 🔲 |\n56: | AR-039-005-C | router | SessionMiddleware | Session middleware attaches session to request | 🔲 |\n57: \n58: ### router 模块 - JWT 认证\n59: \n60: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n61: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n62: | AR-039-006-A | router | JWTManager.GenerateToken | JWT manager creates token with correct claims | 🔲 |\n63: | AR-039-006-B | router | JWTManager.ValidateToken | JWT manager validates valid/expired/invalid tokens | 🔲 |\n64: | AR-039-006-C | router | JWTMiddleware.Middleware | JWT middleware enforces authentication | 🔲 |\n65: \n66: ### router 模块 - 日志和指标\n67: \n68: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n69: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n70: | AR-039-007-A | router | Logger.Middleware | Logger records request details | 🔲 |\n71: | AR-039-007-B | router | Metrics | Metrics records request stats correctly | 🔲 |\n72: \n73: ### store 模块 - Store 接口\n74: \n75: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n76: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n77: | AR-039-008-A | store | Store interface | Store implements complete Store interface | 🔲 |\n78: \n79: ### store 模块 - Valkey Store\n80: \n81: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n82: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n83: | AR-039-009-A | store | newValkeyStore | Valkey store connects with credentials | 🔲 |\n84: | AR-039-009-B | store | newValkeyStore | Valkey store requires VALKEY_ADDR | 🔲 |\n85: | AR-039-009-C | store | StoreSandbox | Valkey store stores sandbox with indices | 🔲 |\n86: | AR-039-009-D | store | GetSandboxBySessionID | Valkey store retrieves sandbox | 🔲 |\n87: | AR-039-009-E | store | GetSandboxBySessionID | Valkey store returns ErrNotFound for non-existent session | 🔲 |\n88: | AR-039-009-F | store | UpdateSandbox | Valkey store updates sandbox | 🔲 |\n89: | AR-039-009-G | store | DeleteSandboxBySessionID | Valkey store deletes sandbox and indices | 🔲 |\n90: | AR-039-009-H | store | ListExpiredSandboxes | Valkey store lists expired sandboxes | 🔲 |\n91: | AR-039-009-I | store | ListInactiveSandboxes | Valkey store lists inactive sandboxes | 🔲 |\n92: | AR-039-009-J | store | StoreSandbox | Valkey store validates input (nil, zero expiry, empty sessionID) | 🔲 |\n93: | AR-039-009-K | store | UpdateSessionLastActivity | Valkey store updates last activity | 🔲 |\n94: | AR-039-009-L | store | Close | Valkey store closes connection | 🔲 |\n95: \n96: ### picod 模块 - Server 初始化\n97: \n98: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n99: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n100: | AR-039-010-A | picod | NewServer | Server creates with valid config | 🔲 |\n101: | AR-039-010-B | picod | NewServer | Server validates config | 🔲 |\n102: | AR-039-010-C | picod | setWorkspace | Server sets workspace directory | 🔲 |\n103: | AR-039-010-D | picod | setWorkspace | Server uses cwd when workspace is empty | 🔲 |\n104: \n105: ### picod 模块 - 路径安全\n106: \n107: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n108: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n109: | AR-039-011-A | picod | sanitizePath | Path sanitization allows safe paths | 🔲 |\n110: | AR-039-011-B | picod | sanitizePath | Path sanitization blocks escape attempts | 🔲 |\n111: | AR-039-011-C | picod | sanitizePath | Path sanitization blocks absolute paths | 🔲 |\n112: | AR-039-011-D | picod | sanitizePath | Path sanitization handles symlinks | 🔲 |\n113: \n114: ### picod 模块 - 认证\n115: \n116: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n117: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n118: | AR-039-012-A | picod | AuthManager | Auth manager loads public key | 🔲 |\n119: | AR-039-012-B | picod | AuthManager.ValidateToken | Auth manager validates JWT | 🔲 |\n120: | AR-039-012-C | picod | AuthManager.ValidateToken | Auth manager rejects invalid JWT | 🔲 |\n121: | AR-039-012-D | picod | Middleware | Auth middleware allows public paths | 🔲 |\n122: | AR-039-012-E | picod | Middleware | Auth middleware requires auth for protected paths | 🔲 |\n123: \n124: ### picod 模块 - Execute Handler\n125: \n126: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n127: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n128: | AR-039-013-A | picod | ExecuteHandler | Execute handler runs valid command | 🔲 |\n129: | AR-039-013-B | picod | ExecuteHandler | Execute handler fails on empty command | 🔲 |\n130: | AR-039-013-C | picod | ExecuteHandler | Execute handler respects timeout | 🔲 |\n131: | AR-039-013-D | picod | ExecuteHandler | Execute handler validates working directory | 🔲 |\n132: | AR-039-013-E | picod | ExecuteHandler | Execute handler captures stderr | 🔲 |\n133: | AR-039-013-F | picod | ExecuteHandler | Execute handler accepts custom environment | 🔲 |\n134: \n135: ### picod 模块 - 文件处理\n136: \n137: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n138: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n139: | AR-039-014-A | picod | UploadFileHandler | Upload file handler saves file | 🔲 |\n140: | AR-039-014-B | picod | ListFilesHandler | List files handler returns directory contents | 🔲 |\n141: | AR-039-014-C | picod | DownloadFileHandler | Download file handler serves file | 🔲 |\n142: | AR-039-014-D | picod | DownloadFileHandler | Download file handler blocks path escape | 🔲 |\n143: \n144: ### picod 模块 - 健康检查和 RSA 密钥\n145: \n146: | ID | Component | Function | Test Scenario | Status |\n147: |----|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|\n148: | AR-039-015-A | picod | HealthCheckHandler | Health check returns healthy status | 🔲 |\n149: | AR-039-015-B | picod | LoadRSAPublicKey | LoadRSAPublicKey parses valid PEM | 🔲 |\n150: | AR-039-015-C | picod | LoadRSAPublicKey | LoadRSAPublicKey rejects invalid PEM | 🔲 |\n151: | AR-039-015-D | picod | LoadRSAPublicKey | LoadRSAPublicKey rejects non-RSA key | 🔲 |\n152: \n153: ---\n154: \n155: ## 测试文件状态\n156: \n157: ### router 模块\n158: \n159: | Source File | Test File | Status |\n160: |-------------|-----------|--------|\n161: | server.go | server_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n162: | config.go | config_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n163: | route.go | route_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n164: | backend.go | backend_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n165: | health.go | health_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n166: | ratelimit.go | ratelimit_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n167: | auth.go | auth_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n168: | session.go | session_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n169: | jwt.go | jwt_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n170: | logging.go | logging_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n171: | metrics.go | (使用已有) | N/A |\n172: \n173: ### store 模块\n174: \n175: | Source File | Test File | Status |\n176: |-------------|-----------|--------|\n177: | store.go | (仅接口) | N/A |\n178: | store_valkey.go | store_valkey_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n179: | store_redis.go | store_redis_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n180: \n181: ### picod 模块\n182: \n183: | Source File | Test File | Status |\n184: |-------------|-----------|--------|\n185: | server.go | server_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n186: | execute.go | execute_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n187: | auth.go | auth_test.go | ✅ 已完成 |\n188: | files.go | files_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n189: | health.go | health_test.go | 🔲 需实现 |\n190: \n191: ---\n192: \n193: ## 验收标准\n194: \n195: - [ ] AC001: Router Config 初始化和默认值测试\n196: - [ ] AC002: Router 创建各种配置组合测试\n197: - [ ] AC003: BackendPool AddBackend, RemoveBackend, GetBackendForRequest 测试\n198: - [ ] AC004: HealthChecker Start, Stop, checkBackend 测试\n199: - [ ] AC005: RateLimiter Allow, Middleware 测试\n200: - [ ] AC006: Authenticator Middleware 启用/禁用状态测试\n201: - [ ] AC007: SessionManager Create, Get, Delete, Cleanup 测试\n202: - [ ] AC008: JWTManager GenerateToken, ValidateToken 测试\n203: - [ ] AC009: JWTMiddleware 各种配置测试\n204: - [ ] AC010: Logger Middleware 测试\n205: - [ ] AC011: Metrics IncBackendRequests, RecordRequestDuration, IncErrors 测试\n206: - [ ] AC012: Valkey store 连接模拟客户端测试\n207: - [ ] AC013: StoreSandbox 有效和无效输入测试\n208: - [ ] AC014: GetSandboxBySessionID 存在/不存在会话测试\n209: - [ ] AC015: UpdateSandbox 测试\n210: - [ ] AC016: DeleteSandboxBySessionID 测试\n211: - [ ] AC017: ListExpiredSandboxes 测试\n212: - [ ] AC018: ListInactiveSandboxes 测试\n213: - [ ] AC019: UpdateSessionLastActivity 测试\n214: - [ ] AC020: Close 测试\n215: - [ ] AC021: Server 创建有效和无效配置测试\n216: - [ ] AC022: setWorkspace 测试\n217: - [ ] AC023: sanitizePath 各种路径输入测试\n218: - [ ] AC024: AuthManager LoadPublicKeyFromEnv, ValidateToken 测试\n219: - [ ] AC025: auth middleware 公共/受保护路径测试\n220: - [ ] AC026: ExecuteHandler 有效命令、超时、无效工作目录测试\n221: - [ ] AC027: UploadFileHandler, ListFilesHandler, DownloadFileHandler 测试\n222: - [ ] AC028: HealthCheckHandler 测试\n223: - [ ] AC029: LoadRSAPublicKey 测试\n224: - [ ] AC030: router, store, picod 包的现有测试保持通过\n225: \n226: ---\n227: \n228: ## 依赖\n229: \n230: - Go 1.21+\n231: - `testing` package (stdlib)\n232: - `github.com/stretchr/testify` - 断言和 mock\n233: - `github.com/golang/mock` 或 `go generate` - mock 生成\n234: - `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` - Valkey 客户端\n235: \n236: ---\n237: \n238: ## 测试模式\n239: \n240: ### Mock 策略\n241: - 对依赖项使用接口 (Store, HTTP clients 等)\n242: - 使用 testify/mock 创建测试 mock\n243: - 对复杂模块使用 gomock 生成 mocks\n244: \n245: ### 测试文件命名\n246: - 遵循 Go 约定: `*_test.go`\n247: - 与被测代码保持在同一包中\n248: - 使用 `package router` (不是 `package router_test`)\n249: \n250: ### 表驱动测试\n251: - 对参数化场景使用表驱动测试\n252: - 示例模式:\n253: ```go\n254: tests := []struct {\n255:     name    string\n256:     input   string\n257:     want    string\n258:     wantErr bool\n259: }{...}\n260: ```\n261: \n262: ### 测试覆盖率目标\n263: - Router 模块: 70%+ 代码覆盖率\n264: - Store 模块: 80%+ 代码覆盖率\n265: - Picod 模块: 70%+ 代码覆盖率\n266: \n267: ---\n268: \n269: ## 参考\n270: \n271: - Router 模块: `pkg/router/`\n272: - Store 模块: `pkg/store/`\n273: - Picod 模块: `pkg/picod/`\n274: - 通用类型: `pkg/common/types/`\n275: - 基础规范 (client-go): `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n\n(End of file - total 275 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) - Delta Spec\n\n> **Module:** pkg\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** L\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing Go unit tests for three core modules:\n- **pkg/router**: HTTP routing, proxy, health checking, rate limiting, authentication, session management, JWT\n- **pkg/store**: Valkey/Redis-backed session and sandbox storage\n- **pkg/picod**: Pico execution server with command execution and file handling\n\n---\n\n## Test Scenarios\n\n### router 模块 - 初始化和配置","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775890193797,"end":1775890193816}}}}
