{"type":"text","timestamp":1775890206987,"sessionID":"ses_284b27354ffetUTuzwDrgNCGp3","part":{"id":"prt_d7b4df098001oRtNpFVGpLCfDK","messageID":"msg_d7b4dddd5001RX66ptrcHLF67b","sessionID":"ses_284b27354ffetUTuzwDrgNCGp3","type":"text","text":"Based on the AR-039 documentation, here's the summary:\n\n## AR-039 归档总结\n\n### ✅ 已完成 (Completed)\n\n**Scaffold & Design (ST-3):**\n- `changes/AR-039/` 目录创建\n- `AR.md` / `proposal.md` / `delta-spec.md` / `tasks.md` / `design.md` 完成\n- 详细的测试场景定义（30 个验收场景）\n- 任务分解（4 个 Phase, 130+ 原子任务）\n\n**Router 模块测试文件 (10/17):**\n- ✅ `config_test.go`, `jwt_test.go`, `session_test.go`\n- ✅ `backend_test.go`, `server_test.go`, `health_test.go`\n- ✅ `logging_test.go`, `auth_test.go`, `ratelimit_test.go`, `route_test.go`\n\n**Picod 模块测试文件 (2/8):**\n- ✅ `auth_config_test.go`, `picod_test.go`\n\n---\n\n### 🔲 延期 (Deferred)\n\n**Router 模块 (7 个文件):**\n- 🔲 `jwt_handler.go`, `jwt_middleware.go`, `jwt_metrics.go`\n- 🔲 `session_middleware.go`, `metrics.go`, `proxy.go`, `informer.go`\n\n**Store 模块 (5 个文件 - 完全未开始):**\n- 🔲 `store.go`, `store_valkey.go`, `store_redis.go`, `singleton.go`, `errors.go`\n\n**Picod 模块 (6 个文件):**\n- 🔲 `config.go`, `execute.go`, `auth.go`, `auth_middleware.go`, `files.go`, `health.go`\n\n---\n\n### 延期原因\n\n1. **Store 模块**: 完全未开始，需要 mock Valkey/Redis 客户端，依赖外部服务\n2. **Router 新增文件**: `jwt_handler`/`jwt_middleware` 等是新增功能模块，尚未稳定\n3. **Picod 剩余文件**: `execute.go`/`files.go` 涉及文件系统和命令执行，测试复杂度高\n\n---\n\n### 建议后续行动\n\n| 优先级 | 模块 | 工作量 | 依赖 |\n|--------|------|--------|------|\n| P1 | Store 模块测试 | ~20 tasks | Mock 客户端已就绪 |\n| P2 | Router 剩余 7 文件 | ~35 tasks | 无外部依赖 |\n| P3 | Picod 剩余 6 文件 | ~25 tasks | 需处理文件系统 mock |","time":{"start":1775890206984,"end":1775890206984}}}
